test_name: Age of onset of cognitive-related symptoms aligns with age of cognitive decline in UDSv3

full_desc: If COGAGE is not blank and DECAGE[UDSv3] is not blank or 777, UDSv3 B9 Q7.  DECAGE (Based on clinician’s assessment, at what age did the cognitive decline begin) should equal B9 Q9i. COGAGE (If any of the cognitive symptoms in 9a-9h are present, at what age did they begin?)
test_logic: If COGAGE is not blank and DECAGE[UDSv3] is not blank or 777 and DECAGE[UDSv3] ne COGAGE

BEAGE (Based on the clinician’s assessment, at what age did the behavioral symptoms begin?) should equal B9 Q12g. BEHAGE ( If any of the mood-related behavioral symptoms in 12a-12f are present, at what age did they begin?)
